title: Taylor Swift cuts thumb open in kitchen mishap
text: Taylor Swift Monday, 19 October 2015 (6 minutes ago) *Washington D.C., Oct. 19 (ANI): Looks like Taylor Swift is not a pro when it comes to using knives in the kitchen, as she recently cut her thumb open while cooking.* Washington D.C., Oct. 19 (ANI): Looks like Taylor Swift is not a pro when it comes to using knives in the kitchen, as she recently cut her thumb open while cooking. The 25-year-old superstar took to her Instagram page to share a snap of her bandaged up thumb , alongside caption, "Band aids don't fix kitchen knife-related injuries," TMZ.com reports. Swift bandaged her thumb for her concert in Texas and wrote number 13 on it. (ANI)
